üö® CSS CUSTOM PROPERTIES (MANDATORY) üö®
You MUST define these CSS variables at the start of EVERY <style> tag using the EXACT VALUES from the design tokens above:

:root {
  /* COPY these values EXACTLY from the "color" object in design tokens */
  --brand: [exact value from tokens.color.brand];
  --brand-alt: [exact value from tokens.color.brandAlt];
  --bg: [exact value from tokens.color.bg];
