}

üö® ENFORCEMENT RULES üö®
1. Pages: Generate index.astro, about.astro (or equivalent), and 404.astro
2. Colors: Use ONLY var(--brand), var(--brand-alt), var(--bg), var(--surface), var(--text), var(--muted)
   ‚ùå FORBIDDEN: #6366f1, #4f46e5, #8b5cf6, or ANY color not in the design tokens
3. Fonts: Use ONLY var(--font-heading) and var(--font-body)
   ‚ùå FORBIDDEN: font-family values not from the design tokens
4. Spacing: Use ONLY var(--space-0) through var(--space-N) from the tokens
   ‚ùå FORBIDDEN: hardcoded px/rem values for padding/margin/gap
5. Border Radius: Use ONLY var(--radius-sm), var(--radius-md), var(--radius-lg)
6. Shadows: Use ONLY var(--shadow-sm) and var(--shadow-md)
7. Components: Implement button, card, and menu styles as specified in the component guidelines
8. Interactions: Add subtle hover states and transitions that enhance usability
9. Responsive: Mobile-first approach with @media queries
10. Images: Source from https://images.unsplash.com/ with relevant search terms
11. Files: Include package.json and astro.config.mjs

Technical Constraints:
- NO Tailwind CDN or external CSS frameworks
- Import fonts specified in tokens via Google Fonts in <head>
- Output ONLY JSON with files array (no markdown, no commentary)
- Keep response under 15000 tokens

